In the 1480s [[DR]],{{ToD-time}} [[Red Wizards]] from [[Thay]] worked alongside the [[Cult of the Dragon]] to perform a powerful ritual that summoned Tiamat's temple―and the goddess Tiamat herself―to the Well of Dragons in [[Faerûn]]. as sacrifice to the Dragon Queen.

The response to the Dragon Cult's actions were profound. An enormous allied army assembled by the [[Council of Waterdeep]] descended upon the Well of Dragons.{{Cite web/Tyranny of Dragons: Online Comic 9}}

Groups of adventurers including the [[Heroes of Sleeping Dragon Bridge]] defeated the Red Wizard that summoned Tiamat to her temple, and defended the [[cleric]]s working with [[Linu La'neral]] to inflict vulnerability upon the Dragon Goddess. Eventually Tiamat was sent back down to the Nine Hells, and adventurers representing the [[Five Factions]] of the Sword Coast abducted Severin himself.{{Cite web/Tyranny of Dragons: Online Comic 10}}
